OL,3,C'Deeply worrying' police data shows
OL,4,Csharp rise in religious hate crimes
OL,5,Cafter Israel-Gaza war
OL,7,FThe number of antisemitic hate crimes
OL,8,Frecorded by many of the UK's largest
OL,9,Fpolice forces jumped sharply in the
OL,10,Fweeks following the outbreak of the
OL,11,FHamas-Israel conflict, new figures
OL,12,Freveal.
OL,14,FIslamophobic offences also rose for
OL,15,Fsome forces, although the picture was
OL,16,Fmore mixed across the country.
OL,18,FJewish charities called the findings
OL,19,F"shocking", while campaigners against
OL,20,Fanti-Muslim abuse said the data was
OL,21,F"deeply worrying".
